  "extra_note_en": "The synthetic future (falarei) is less common in spoken Brazilian Portuguese — most people say 'vou falar' instead (near/planned future). Use the synthetic form more in formal writing, predictions ('Choverá amanhã' = It will rain tomorrow), promises, or European Portuguese. Very frequent irregulars: dizer → direi, fazer → farei, trazer → trarei, poder → poderei, saber → saberei, querer → quererei, caber → caberei, haver → haverei, pôr → porei, valer → valerei. Time expressions: amanhã (tomorrow), na próxima semana (next week), logo (soon), daqui a pouco (in a little while), no futuro (in the future), etc."
